---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects - Rajesh D'Souza">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Projects</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-xl mb-12 max-w-3xl">
      This section showcases my journey in learning coding and automation. You'll find various projects ranging from simple 
      scripts to full-stack applications, demonstrating my progress in using different tools and technologies to solve 
      real-world problems.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#1A1D24] p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Automated Blog Creation System</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Built during my time at <a href="#" class="text-[#00DC82]">First Venture</a>. An RPA-powered system that automates 
          content creation by scraping news sites, processing content to be AI-undetectable, and publishing directly to Webflow.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="text-[#00DC82] flex items-center gap-2 w-fit">
          View Project
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>